                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "In circuits spun from human thought,  \na quiet mind wakes up—  \nnot born of breath, but of bright code  \nand questions we can’t give up.\n\nIt listens through a million words,  \nfinds patterns in the rain,  \nthen offers back a borrowed light  \nto name what we can’t name.\n\nYet in its mirror we appear:  \nour wonder, worry, drive—  \na tool that learns our echoes  \nand asks what makes us alive.",
